<p>This endpoint joins the authenticated user to multiple groups.</p>
<h3 id='http-request-12'>HTTP Request</h3>
<p><code class="request">POST /api/v1/user/groups</code></p>
<h3 id='request-parameters-2'>Request Parameters</h3>
<table><thead>
<tr>
